description: The distant sound of crashing waves filters in on the cooler breeze present near the lagoon edge.  Several tall trees provide a backdrop to the foliage that spreads out from the shore, creating a thick canopy of leaves that sway with the breeze and help to break the sunlight into less intense, variegated shafts of heat.
title: [Saewehna Lagoon, Shore]
location: the environs of the Saewehna Lagoon
